11. Error Handling in Automation
def safe_execute(action, employee):
    try:
        action(employee)
    except Exception as e:
        log_error(employee["id"], str(e))
        retry_queue.add(employee)
12. Retry & Recovery Logic
Failed IAM provisioning → retry 3 times
Workflow failure → rollback transaction
API failure → queue event for replay
Audit always recorded (even on failure)
